          "A fragment context must be selected before local node focus can be interpreted.",
          "A focused node inside the selected fragment needs to become the center before ring distance can be interpreted.",
          "Nodes directly connected to the center need a stable second-ring representation.",
          "Nodes one connection farther out need a third-ring representation that can upgrade from type badge to icon-view as they load.",
          "Nodes one more connection out need a stable fourth-ring dot representation.",
          "Loader order must proceed outward inside the selected fragment by ring.",
          "Cached data may satisfy a ring immediately, but must not exceed the representation cap for that ring.",
          "User focus must be more precise than fragment selection.",
          "A runtime-generated root may still project sibling `.node` files as discovered children for folder browsing."
